{"tid":1971550,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【坡狗又贏 Failed DOG】新加坡CnVID-19疫情創失控 單日新增400例創新高","createTime":"2020-04-14T03:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T06:55:33.000Z","uid":242537,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7b0eccc889135755e6e83a29e51b2f82619e4c","tid":1971550,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202004140002.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202004140002.aspx&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=01064819\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202004140002.aspx</a><br />\n新加坡今晚公佈最新2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情數字，新增武漢肺炎確診386起，再創單日新高，同時增加4個感染群。新加坡確診累計2918例。<br />\n<br />\n新增的386起病例全是本土感染病例，其中280起與現有感染群有關，有12起與先前確診病例有關，另有94起暫與其他病例無關。<br />\n<br />\n今天新增的4個感染群中，有2個在外籍勞工宿舍。新加坡今天也出現第9起的死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡今天有超過200人因沒有遵守社交安全距離措施遭到罰款。另外，第一批共31名身體健康的外籍勞工搬入丹戎巴葛貨櫃碼頭的海上浮動宿舍，接下來數週也會有約1300名身體健康的外勞陸續搬進浮動宿舍。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KgLv6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KgLv6Q.jpg&h=281d7122&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0346b250dc5e0d841b2e763fd8ef8eb5aad936a","tid":1971550,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"點鬥啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282f1e446911364d25c568d0a52bf3c4cf20b6b5","tid":1971550,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"就快係香港3倍"},{"pid":"0accfe3bf8f092ba360403942f62b52610d664c7","tid":1971550,"uid":172627,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔夠我地新加坡鬥！</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔夠我地新加坡鬥！</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔夠我地新加坡鬥！</span>唔夠我地新加坡鬥！"},{"pid":"7160029bb2e9af08587